Third-party components installed at runtime (not redistributed in this tree)
================================================================================

The following components are fetched or installed locally during skill setup
(`scripts/install-*.sh`, per-skill `scripts/post-install.sh`). Their licenses
apply when they are present on a user's machine. They are NOT distributed by
this repository.

2. gstack browse binary
   - Used by: kr-naver-browse, kr-naver-blogger, kr-naver-insight,
     kr-naver-blog-publish, kr-web-browse, kr-analyst-report-* skills
   - Fetched into: skills/kr-naver-browse/vendor/gstack/ at install time
   - License: MIT
   - Upstream: https://github.com/garrytan/gstack

3. pypdf (Python package)
   - Used by: skills/kr-stock-dart-analysis/scripts/extract-pdf-text.py
     (also reused by kr-analyst-report-fetch)
   - Install: python3 -m pip install pypdf
   - License: BSD-3-Clause
   - Upstream: https://github.com/py-pdf/pypdf

4. Pillow (PIL fork, Python package)
   - Used by: chart text rendering on macOS/Linux in
     skills/kr-stock-chart/scripts/chart-basics.js and
     skills/kr-stock-analysis/scripts/valuation-chart.js (via Python helper)
   - Install: python3 -m pip install pillow
   - License: HPND (PIL Software License)
   - Upstream: https://github.com/python-pillow/Pillow

5. Bun (JavaScript runtime)
   - Used by: kr-naver-browse post-install to build the gstack browse binary
   - Install: handled by skills/kr-naver-browse/scripts/post-install.sh
   - License: MIT
   - Upstream: https://github.com/oven-sh/bun

================================================================================
Data sources accessed at runtime
================================================================================

Skills in this repository call third-party HTTP endpoints. Users are responsible
for complying with each provider's terms of service and rate limits.

- OpenDART (dart.fss.or.kr) — requires OPENDART_API_KEY
- Yahoo Finance (query2.finance.yahoo.com) — used by fetch-kr-chart.js
- Hankyung Consensus (consensus.hankyung.com) — used by kr-analyst-report-discover
- Naver Pay Research (finance.naver.com/research) — fallback in kr-analyst-report-discover
- Naver Search / Naver Blog / Naver News — used by kr-naver-* and kr-foreign-analyst
- Naver SmartEditor (blog.naver.com) — used by kr-naver-blog-publish (browser automation)
